---
import Icon from './Icon.astro';
---

<section class="box skills">
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="strategy" color="#48769e" size="2.5rem" />
		<h2>EU Compliance<br />& AI Ethics</h2>
		<p>With a background in Human Rights Law and working knowledge of DAMA data management principles, I work with the regulatory frameworks that shape how organizations handle data and AI responsibly — EU AI Act, GDPR, FRIA, and human rights-based approaches to bias detection, privacy risks, and ethical impact assessments.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="microphone-stage" color="#48769e" size="2.5rem" />
		<h2>Communication & Training</h2>
		<p>I turn complex frameworks into clear, accessible language that sticks. Through storytelling, tailored workshops, and hands-on training, I make sure every team — legal, HR, operations, leadership — not only understands what governance requires, but knows how to apply it. And because I work with the technical tools myself, I know exactly where people get lost — and how to bring them back.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="code" color="#48769e" size="2.5rem" />
		<h2>Data-driven Governance</h2>
		<p>I use SQL, Python, and Power BI to build dashboards and KPI frameworks that make governance visible — turning policy into measurable business outcomes and giving leadership the evidence they need to make informed decisions.</p>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.box {
		border: 1px solid #48769e;
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background-color: var(--gray-999);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
	}

	.skills {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3rem;
	}

	.skills h2 {
		font-size: var(--text-lg);
		font-family: var(--font-brand);
		color: var(--gray-0);
	}

	.skills p {
		color: var(--gray-300);
		font-family: var(--font-body);
	}

	:global(.theme-dark) .skills p {
		color: #c4aaa0;
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.box {
			border-radius: 1.5rem;
			padding: 2.5rem;
		}

		.skills {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
			gap: 5rem;
		}

		.skills h2 {
			font-size: var(--text-2xl);
		}
	}
</style>
